===================================== GOAL =====================================

  Automatized the analysis of an application


===================================== USAGE ====================================

usage: analysis.py [-h] [--emulator EMULATOR] [--phone PHONE] [--proxy PROXY]
                   [--proxy_cert PROXY_CERT]
                   app

Analysis for smartphone

positional arguments:
  app                   app target <filename.apk>

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit

dynamic:
  --emulator EMULATOR   path of the emulator if used
  --phone PHONE         phones target emulator -list-avds
  --proxy PROXY         setup proxy address <ip>:<port>
  --proxy_cert PROXY_CERT
                        setup proxy address <filename>.cer


=================================== EXEMPLE ====================================

python3 analysis.py <example>.apk --emulator ~/Android/Sdk/tools/ \
        --phone Pixel_3a_XL_API_22 --proxy 127.0.0.1:8080 --proxy_cert burp.der

# To list all emulator phone avaible
emulator -list-avds

